       "      )\n",
       "      (cls_logits): Conv2d(256, 3, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))\n",
       "      (bbox_pred): Conv2d(256, 12, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))\n",
