    "## Charecterstics\n",
    "\n",
    "### Why Mask R-CNN Was Important\n",
    "\n",
    "Before Mask R-CNN:\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "Object Detection: Rectangle only\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "After:\n",
    "\n",
    "```text\n",
    "Pixel-level object understanding\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "Huge improvement for scene understanding.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Applications\n",
    "\n",
    "* Autonomous vehicles  \n",
    "  Segment:\n",
    "  * pedestrians\n",
    "  * vehicles\n",
    "  * roads\n",
    "* Medical imaging\n",
    "  Segment:\n",
    "  * tumors\n",
    "  * organs\n",
    "* Satellite imagery\n",
    "  Segment:\n",
    "  * roads\n",
    "  * buildings\n",
    "* Robotics\n",
    "  * Separate objects for manipulation.\n",
    "* Image editing\n",
    "  * Background removal and object selection.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Advantages\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Accurate instance segmentation: Pixel-level masks.\n",
    "2. Builds on Faster R-CNN: Uses proven architecture.\n",
    "3. ROI Align improves precision: Removes quantization error.\n",
    "4. Multi-task learning: Detection and segmentation together.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Limitations\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Computationally expensive: Additional mask branch increases cost.\n",
    "2. Slower than single-stage detectors  \n",
    "  Examples:\n",
    "   * YOLO\n",
    "   * SSD\n",
    "3. Requires pixel-level annotations: Mask labels are expensive to create.\n",
    "\n"
